content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #88236 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

after a quick rust.godbolt.org rundown this issue doesn't look like a regression, the ICE has always been there. Is this a case of a missing/failed diagnostics?
I'd say P-low or P-medium, depending on how easily people could trip on this

Indeed, for a second I was worried I caused this with my normalization changes. But saw that it also occurred on stable (albeit with a "different" ICE). I say P-medium. Seems somewhat easy enough to hit.
